msgstr "不審なIP アドレスからのアクセス制限"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:1
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/controls.jsx:249
msgid ""
"This refers to restricting access from suspicious IP addresses, such as "
"those from overseas, using firewalls, WAFs, apps, etc."
msgstr ""
"ファイアウォールやWAF、アプリ等によって、海外等の不審なIPアドレスからのアクセ"
"ス制限を行うことを指します。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:1
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/controls.jsx:261
msgid "Identity verification using two-factor authentication, etc."
msgstr "二要素認証等による本人確認など。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:1
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/controls.jsx:266
msgid ""
"This refers to increasing security strength by combining multiple levels or "
"elements of authentication, such as biometric authentication using "
"fingerprints or faces, or email or SMS authentication, in addition to ID and "
"password."
msgstr ""
"ID・パスワードに加え、指紋や顔による生体認証またはメール・SMS認証などの複数の"
"段階または要素の認証を組み合わせることで、セキュリティ強度を高めることを指し"
"ます。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:1
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/controls.jsx:278
