msgstr "デバイスフィンガープリント等。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:1
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/controls.jsx:299
msgid ""
"This technology tracks online behavior by using the characteristics of the "
"operating environment of the user's device as a kind of fingerprint."
msgstr ""
"ユーザーが使うデバイス（端末）の動作環境の特徴を、フィンガープリント（指紋）"
"のように手掛かりにして、ネット上の行動を追跡する技術です。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:1
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/controls.jsx:312
msgid ""
"If there is more than one question with a \"yes\" answer, please provide an "
"alternative solution."
msgstr "「はい」が１つ以上つかない設問がある場合、代替策を記入してください。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:1
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/controls.jsx:325
msgid ""
"We have not received any administrative penalties under the Specified "
"Commercial Transactions Law in the past five years."
msgstr "直近5年間、特定商取引法に基づく行政処分を受けていない。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:1
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/controls.jsx:348
msgid ""
"I have never been sued in a civil lawsuit or received an unfavorable "
"judgment based on actions that violated the Consumer Contract Act."
msgstr ""
"消費者契約法違反の行為を理由として民事上の訴訟を提訴され、敗訴判決を受けたこ"
"とがない。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:1
#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:5
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:46
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/index.js:30
msgid "Easy setup for Paidy payment"
msgstr "ペイディ決済らくらく設定"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:1
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:54
msgid "Paidy application"
msgstr "ペイディ申し込み"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:1
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:65
msgid "Get started now"
msgstr "今すぐ始める"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:1
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:77
msgid "I agree to the above and apply"
msgstr "上記内容で申し込む"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:3
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:152
msgid "Basic information"
msgstr "基本情報"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:3
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:221
msgid "Security survey"
msgstr "セキュリティアンケート"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:3
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:224
msgid ""
"Based on requests from the Ministry of Economy, Trade and Industry and the "
"Japan Consumer Credit Association, all e-commerce affiliates are required to "
"declare the status of their own security measures when joining. Please "
"answer the following questions."
msgstr ""
"経済産業省および日本クレジット協会からの要請に基づき、全てのEC加盟店はご加盟"
"時に自らのセキュリティ対策の措置状況の申告が必要となるため、以下の設問にご回"
"答をお願いします。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:3
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:231
msgid ""
"For details, please refer to <link>the Security Measures Status Declaration "
"Form FAQ.</link>"
msgstr ""
"詳細は<link>セキュリティ対策状況申告フォームFAQ</link>をご参照ください。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:3
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:247
msgid ""
"*If the system has not yet been built, please declare the check items for "
"each security measure on the assumption that they will be satisfied once the "
"system is built."
msgstr ""
"※システム未構築の場合は、各セキュリティ対策のチェック項目について、構築完了し"
"た時点で充足することを前提に申告してください。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:3
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:255
msgid "[Measures to prevent leakage of cardholder data]"
msgstr "【カード会員データの漏えい対策】"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:3
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:280
msgid "[Countermeasures against unauthorized logins]"
msgstr "【不正ログイン対策】"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:3
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:286
msgid ""
"*At least one \"Yes\" is required. If any are missing, we will contact you."
msgstr ""
"※「はい」が１つ以上必要です。不足がある場合、弊社からご連絡いたします。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:3
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:293
msgid ""
"Do you take the following measures to prevent unauthorized logins when "
"changing a user's attributes?"
msgstr "ユーザーの『属性変更時』に以下の不正ログイン対策を行っていますか ?"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:3
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:329
msgid "Questionnaire"
msgstr "アンケート"

#. translators: %s: plugin name
#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:4
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:411
msgid "Easy Paidy setup now available with %s!"
msgstr "%sでペイディ決済らくらく設定、はじまりました !"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:4
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:419
msgid "Right now, we are offering a one-month trial with no payment fees!"
msgstr "今なら、なんとお試し1か月決済手数料無料！"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:4
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:440
msgid "What is Paidy?"
msgstr "ペイディって？"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:4
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:442
msgid ""
"Paidy is a deferred payment service that can be used without the need for a "
"credit card."
msgstr "Paidyは、クレジットカード不要で使える“あと払い”決済です。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:4
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:447
msgid ""
"Customers can make purchases with just their mobile phone number and email "
"address."
msgstr "購入者は、携帯番号とメールアドレスだけでお買い物。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:4
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:452
msgid ""
"Payment can be made from the following month onwards via convenience store, "
"bank or direct debit."
msgstr "支払いは翌月以降に、コンビニ・銀行・口座振替でOK。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:4
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:457
msgid "We respond to the desire to \"buy now.\""
msgstr "「今すぐ買いたい」気持ちにこたえます。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:4
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:471
msgid "Benefits of implementation (for EC businesses)"
msgstr "導入のメリット（EC事業者向け）"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:4
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:476
msgid ""
"No credit card registration is required, making it easy for new customers to "
"make purchases with confidence."
msgstr "クレカ登録なしでOKだから、新規のお客様が安心して購入しやすくなります。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:4
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:481
msgid ""
"Installment payments are also supported, which is expected to increase the "
"success rate of high-priced products."
msgstr "分割払いにも対応しているため、高単価商品の成約率アップが期待できます。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:4
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:486
msgid ""
"*Free installment fees only apply when paying by direct debit or bank "
"transfer. Identity verification and app download required."
msgstr ""
"※分割手数料無料は口座振替・銀行払い時のみ。本人認証とアプリDLが必要です。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:4
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:491
msgid ""
"Currently used on over 700,000 websites nationwide, including Amazon. "
"Industry-leading track record."
msgstr ""
"Amazonをはじめ、全国70万以上のサイトで利用中。 業界トップクラスの実績。"

#. translators: %s: plugin name
#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:5
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:502
msgid "%s * Paidy"
msgstr "%s × Paidy"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:5
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:507
msgid ""
"With this update, Paidy can now be installed in as little as 30 seconds!"
msgstr "今回のアップデートで、Paidyが最短30秒で導入可能に！"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:5
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:512
msgid "No initial or monthly fees."
msgstr "初期費用・月額費用ゼロ。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:5
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:517
msgid ""
"The review process is completed in as little as 1-2 days, and setup is easy."
msgstr "審査も最短1〜2日で完了、設定もカンタンです。"

#: assets/js/build/paidy/wizard/paidy.js:5
#: src/js/paidy/wizard/components/first-main-page.jsx:530
msgid "pass this time"
msgstr "今回は見送る"

